    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers short, precise throws, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. This example benefits from documented subframe reinforcement and a recent valve clearance adjustment, ensuring mechanical longevity. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings, providing communicative steering through the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup. A mechanically sound, driver-focused machine with a clean title and comprehensive service history.",
