      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for performance coupe that strikes the perfect balance between exhilarating driveability and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front fascia and a few light surface marks consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a premium sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple and free of any tears or odors, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle has been treated with the utmost respect. It features a complete service history, with a recent comprehensive fluid flush and a fresh set of high-performance tires installed within the last few months. The engine pulls strongly and smoothly, while the transmission offers crisp, confident shifts. This is a turn-key vehicle, perfect for the enthusiast who wants a well-documented, reliable car that is ready for the open road.",
